(105, 1, 105, 1, 1, 1, '2023-01-05 13:41:07', '2023-03-13 14:34:50', 0, 34, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '0', '0', '#000', '0', 'typeU', '', '', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b style=\"\"><font color=\"#3984c6\">▶	出入公共場所要注意\r\n</font></b></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">出入人多的地方務必戴好口罩，接觸食物前請務必洗淨雙手，並且避免與他人共食</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br></span>\r\n</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b style=\"\"><font color=\"#3984c6\" style=\"\">▶	落實洗手步驟，剔除危險病毒殘留機會\r\n</font></b></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><font color=\"#3984c6\">1.	專用洗潔劑 ➙&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\">破壞病毒的細胞膜，殺死病毒</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><font color=\"#3984c6\">2.	內部清潔 ➙&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\">掌心對掌心</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><font color=\"#3984c6\">3.	外部清潔 ➙&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\">掌心對掌背</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><font color=\"#3984c6\">4.	指縫清潔 ➙&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\">十指縫隙交互搓揉</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><font color=\"#3984c6\">5.	指背清潔 ➙&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\">手心與手指背交互搓揉</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><font color=\"#3984c6\">6.	虎口清潔 ➙&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\">大拇指對虎口轉動清潔</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><font color=\"#3984c6\">7.	指尖清潔 ➙&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\">手指立起對掌心搓揉指間</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><font color=\"#3984c6\">8.	手腕清潔 ➙&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\">搓到手腕部位清潔</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">※ 強化「搓」動作，請